    <title>条款2: 替换#define</title>
    <url>/2023/02/27/EffectiveC-%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0-2023-02-27-%E6%9D%A1%E6%AC%BE2-%E6%9B%BF%E6%8D%A2-define/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="尽量以const-enum-inline替换-define"><a href="#尽量以const-enum-inline替换-define" class="headerlink" title="尽量以const, enum, inline替换#define"></a>尽量以const, enum, inline替换#define</h1><hr>
<h2 id="为什么要替换-define"><a href="#为什么要替换-define" class="headerlink" title="为什么要替换#define"></a>为什么要替换#define</h2><p>假设有存在一个定义</p>
<figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">define</span> PI_M 3.1415</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><code>PI_M</code>在编译前就被预处理器移走了, 所以从未进入过<code>symbol table</code>, 如果在使用变量但是出现编译期错误信息时, 提到的是<code>3.1415</code>而不是<code>PI_M</code>, 同理在<code>symbol debugger</code>中也可能因为没有进入<code>symbol table</code>而为了追踪它浪费时间</p>
<p><em><strong>解决方法</strong></em></p>
<p>用常量代替宏</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">const double PI_M = 3.1415;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><em><strong>注意:</strong></em> C++98中规定, 在<code>命名空间 namespace</code>中的const是隐式static的</p>
<blockquote>
<p><em>Translation unit:</em> A source file after the pre-processor (recursively) included all its include files.</p>
<p><em>Static linkage:</em> A symbol is only available within its translation unit.</p>
<p><em>External linkage:</em> A symbol is available from other translation units.</p>
</blockquote>
<figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">static</span> <span class="type">const</span> <span class="type">int</span> sci = <span class="number">0</span>; <span class="comment">// sci is explicitly static</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">const</span> <span class="type">int</span> ci = <span class="number">1</span>;         <span class="comment">// ci is implicitly static</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">extern</span> <span class="type">const</span> <span class="type">int</span> eci = <span class="number">2</span>; <span class="comment">// eci is explicitly extern</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">extern</span> <span class="type">int</span> ei = <span class="number">3</span>;        <span class="comment">// ei is explicitly extern</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> i = <span class="number">4</span>;                <span class="comment">// i is implicitly extern</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">static</span> <span class="type">int</span> si = <span class="number">5</span>;        <span class="comment">// si is explicitly static</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>使用宏可能由于预处理器的替换是盲目的, 可能在object code中出现多份3.1415, 而const绝对不会</p>
<h4 id=""><a href="#" class="headerlink" title=""></a></h4>]]></content>
